  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "0238ee09bfd63cceaaff7637f28267b412704133a78f7ce57f73508fe8ff020e": "Have you talked to the citizens yet, [?]?",
    "0cd7c7ea9397ec18962028bf3f5020de80f4a9e37d2caaba7ddb891056fb2f42": "Thank you, [?]. You've shown yourself to be an excellent diplomat and warrior - not a combination that comes naturally to many.",
    "0e32f4b1d71a16379f89c370772e97e670fb7a39ae6c6ff749f97093cce4dada": "It's one of the hazards of ruling a country, [?].",
    "89c3923aa4fdf3aa7711f877e52c5383dbf04285f791a4f912b25df6dd2f111c": "Thank you for all your help, [?]. To show our gratitude, the woodcutters and other workers of Etceteria have pledged to add a proportion of what they produce to your treasury.",
    "f786ca53ec2e568d99762c0977d01497a6018f3b55785134b27e0232562183c7": "Thank you for all your help, [?]. It's good to know that the Regent of Miscellania is willing to help his neighbours."
  }
}